   "source": [
    "# for...of loop\n",
    "It goes through a list (array or string) one item at a time"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0d242c64-d521-4acb-bcef-ce140e46517c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "```javascript\n",
    "for (let num of numbers)\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5b4d0140-12a1-49a6-8207-0a14b3fd86aa",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Don’t use else when you want to keep checking more possibilities"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8e750acf-d676-4d59-adfd-a5a1b5034e2c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "for...of → gives you VALUES\n",
    "for...in → gives you KEYS / INDEXES"
   ]
  },
